sep=: Story Title
As a developer I want to see documentation on how the search was set up.
As a visitor I want a reasonable result my search does not bring up any exact result match.
As a visitor I want to be able to search a specific podcast using multiple keyword argument
As a visitor I want to be able to search a specific podcast using a single keyword argument
As a visitor I want to get reasonable search results back from my search queries.
As a visitor I want a google-like search tool that is intuitive and easy to use.
As a developer I want to access an open source API to get data for my own application.
As a visitor I want to be able to filter the results to find what I want.
As a visitor I want to view the instances of the models with pages for a better viewing experience.
As a visitor I want to be able to use search on the website to find details about a podcast, episode, genre, or host.
As a visitor I want to be able to use the navigation bar from anywhere in the site
As a visitor I want to be able to see featured podcasts when I visit the site
As a developer I want to be able to view an UML diagram in the project report to learn about the database design for the website
As a developer I want to be able to get all the project requirements from a central file
As a developer I want to be able to interpret a json file from the backend api request
As a developer I want to be able to view source code and run the app quickly and across different platforms with reactjs
As a visitor I want to view a website with styling for viewing enjoyment
As a developer I want to query a database to get back data.
As a developer I want to read the project report to learn about the development process for creating the website
As a viewer I want to see a modern website design for readability and ease of use
As a developer I want a stable GCP server instance so that I can reliably access the website
As a visitor I want to be able to see GitHub statistics about the development team that worked on the website
As a visitor I want to be able to see rich content media about podcasts
As a visitor I want to view various podcast pages to learn about them
As a developer I want to query api data that comes from multiple sources
As a visitor I want to view podcast information in a structured way
As a visitor I want to understand the team info in an ordered way
As a visitor I want to view 5 different podcast attributes so that I can learn more about a podcast
As a visitor I want to click on the about to learn more about the team.
As a developer I want to view documentation to query my own requests to get data
